	<LINE>THE GLASGOW HIGH SCHOOL CLUB.</LINE>
	<LINE>The objects of the club are generally to promote</LINE>
	<LINE>the interests of the High School, especially by the</LINE>
	<LINE>establishment of prizes in the shape of scholarships.</LINE>
	<LINE>All who have attended the Glasgow Grammar School,</LINE>
	<LINE>or the High School of Glasgow, are eligible as mem-</LINE>
	<LINE>bers upon payment of 21s. There is no annual</LINE>
	<LINE>subscription. President, J. Cleland Burns Esq.,</LINE>
	<LINE>vice-presidents, Robert Gourlay, Esq. and J. 0.</LINE>
	<LINE>Mitchell, Esq.; treasurer, Jas. Brown, 98 Mitchell St.;</LINE>
	<LINE>secretary, T. 0. Niven, C.E., 115 Wellington Street.</LINE>
