	<LINE>J. Young, Esq., of Kelly, trustees ; Jas. Bryan, Esq.,</LINE>
	<LINE>president; Bruce B. Blackwood, treasurer; John</LINE>
	<LINE>Sutherland, secretary; Alex. Mair, D. Miller, P.</LINE>
	<LINE>Connel, D. Greer, Dr. M'Innes, James Eiddell, Alex.</LINE>
	<LINE>Taylor, Joseph Watt, George Morton, Archibald C.</LINE>
