	<LINE>WEAVING BRANCH — WELL STREET, CALTON.</LINE>
	<LINE>Trustees, Col. W. M. Neilson, of QueenshiU ; Col.</LINE>
	<LINE>Holms, M.P. ; James Templeton, Esq., 7 Woodside</LINE>
	<LINE>Crescent; David Sandeman, Esq., John Street; S.</LINE>
	<LINE>Mason, Esq., Queen Street; Secretary, Eobt. Frame,</LINE>
	<LINE>98 Bath Street; Instnictor, James M'Aulay, Well</LINE>
